replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑色細嗰隻幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一張圖？歲半"},{"pid":"aca3e8a00fd6c7271a26adaa943e29281b691e9d","tid":227542,"uid":93547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黑色細嗰隻幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一張圖？歲半</blockquote><br />\n第二張圖"},{"pid":"f988cfccf589e9f4ef57fad46a457f7e9adc2cff","tid":227542,"uid":98529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黑色細嗰隻幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一張圖？歲半</blockquote><br />\n第二張圖</blockquote><br />\n舊圖黎，影果時黑色8個月，棕色4個月"},{"pid":"31e6424e6151054e6eaa7ea350ef0acb70aba845","tid":227542,"uid":103907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下面個2隻咩品種  係咪有mix過？</blockquote><br />\n啊拉斯加雪橇犬，冇mix過</blockquote><br />\n冷氣費幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n唔洗開冷氣，佢會慣.夠通風就得</blockquote><br />\n咁你自己有冇開？ 你習唔習慣？"},{"pid":"8d99a26bc84241e9cc9d56e19cfefde814409dec","tid":227542,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"我跑開嗰度成日有隻husky(not mal)<br />\n我走埋去同佢玩，咬到我隻手全部都係印，係好痛嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個工人話佢係咁，成日比佢老細屌<br />\n係咪husky都係咁同大人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無流血<br />\n然後好多咬狗事件都係husky<br />\n以前好鍾意佢地個樣，近年有啲改觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c442fb8294822f05e0e2120159420b61cd04ec7","tid":227542,"uid":98529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下面個2隻咩品種  係咪有mix過？</blockquote><br />\n啊拉斯加雪橇犬，冇mix過</blockquote><br />\n冷氣費幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n唔洗開冷氣，佢會慣.夠通風就得</blockquote><br />\n咁你自己有冇開？ 你習唔習慣？</blockquote><br />\n唔好扲人黎同狗比，你長期開冷氣佢慣左有冷氣只會令佢出街更辛苦，你有辦法確保佢24小時都有冷氣不中斷？聽過有狗仔屋企就係24小時開冷氣，有日突然斷電冇左冷氣，隻狗就中暑死左"},{"pid":"1842e4ab89b03ec91d40b57d24fad026658935cb","tid":227542,"uid":75373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"用一個尿盆定兩個"},{"pid":"9888e8e4a80bebaaf85f5da2c665dc73c3c878d7","tid":227542,"uid":98529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我跑開嗰度成日有隻husky(not mal)<br />\n我走埋去同佢玩，咬到我隻手全部都係印，係好痛嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個工人話佢係咁，成日比佢老細屌<br />\n係咪husky都係咁同大人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無流血<br />\n然後好多咬狗事件都係husky<br />\n以前好鍾意佢地個樣，近年有啲改觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHusky性格好古怪，佢要好大既運動量至夠，咬人隻手係因為主人冇去教，淨係識話佢係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咬狗/打交大多两個原因，佢運動量唔夠，佢就會揾地方發洩，咬野/打交，而打交係發洩最好既方法，另外原因，狗仔之間會有地位之分，大家唔服大家就會用打交黎解決，，仲有小型犬睇地位睇得好重要，所以好多時都係啲小型犬走去撩隻大狗，大狗先發惡"},{"pid":"855424d3f5c2204adb53525edf6da78ad7164468","tid":227542,"uid":98529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用一個尿盆定兩個</blockquote><br />\n出街柯"},{"pid":"f213bd88d5966621f7706601dc96c3d3ead06338","tid":227542,"uid":31588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"一個月要洗幾錢？ 係咪三隻都食一樣既糧？"},{"pid":"90df5231f99948e202f215627fb6fe9dfac1d811","tid":227542,"uid":98529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T21:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月要洗幾錢？ 係咪三隻都食一樣既糧？</blockquote><br />\n6000有找，食唔同糧睇下佢適合邊種先"},{"pid":"f9452f878035acb11f1916e2b7ae04b1835c04d9","tid":227542,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我跑開嗰度成日有隻husky(not mal)<br />\n我走埋去同佢玩，咬到我隻手全部都係印，係好痛嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個工人話佢係咁，成日比佢老細屌<br />\n係咪husky都係咁同大人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無流血<br />\n然後好多咬狗事件都係husky<br />\n以前好鍾意佢地個樣，近年有啲改觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHusky性格好古怪，佢要好大既運動量至夠，咬人隻手係因為主人冇去教，淨係識話佢係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咬狗/打交大多两個原因，佢運動量唔夠，佢就會揾地方發洩，咬野/打交，而打交係發洩最好既方法，另外原因，狗仔之間會有地位之分，大家唔服大家就會用打交黎解決，，仲有小型犬睇地位睇得好重要，所以好多時都係啲小型犬走去撩隻大狗，大狗先發惡</blockquote><br />\n佢已經係成犬size ，唔出血都痛到pk<br />\n咁可以點教？<br />\n個工人話隻狗剩係唔咬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又真係係比佢摸嗰陣唔會咬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但金毛嗰啲比狗挑機多數都仲好happy(有代人養過一排，成日都好柒好開心咁，你屌佢即刻sad樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHusky屌都唔係好理咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會都關品種事，金毛係尋回血都係大運動量型"},{"pid":"74ee2c63cd4898d011ab17556a90eb5cf47238be","tid":227542,"uid":98529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我跑開嗰度成日有隻husky(not mal)<br />\n我走埋去同佢玩，咬到我隻手全部都係印，係好痛嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個工人話佢係咁，成日比佢老細屌<br />\n係咪husky都係咁同大人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無流血<br />\n然後好多咬狗事件都係husky<br />